In [7]:
img=cv2.imread(path+'lena.tif',0)
arr=np.asarray(img)
ds={}
plt.figure(figsize=(20,20))
for i in range(7,-1,-1):
    ds["bp{0}".format(i)]=np.zeros(np.shape(arr),dtype='uint8')
    bit=2**i
    for j in range(np.shape(arr)[0]):
        for k in range(np.shape(arr)[1]):
            if arr[j,k]>=bit:
                arr[j,k]=arr[j,k]-bit
                ds["bp{0}".format(i)][j,k]=bit
    plt.subplot(2,4,8-i)
    plt.title("bit plane {0}".format(i))
    plt.imshow(ds["bp{0}".format(i)],'gray')
plt.tight_layout()
